# Exploration: fmt

## Test scope
  162 behavioral groups: 94 unique, 68 shared

  Contexts referenced in exemplars below:
    numbers_standard / input.txt=size:1: standard structure, 1-byte input file
    passwd_minimal / stdin: piped input via stdin
    words_minimal: 1500 English words; input.txt + other.txt
    words_minimal / stdin: piped input via stdin

## Observed: 7/7 flags
  3 uniquely observable, 4 distinguishable via flag pairs
  1 behavioral aliases (different flags, identical behavior)
  robustness: 9 verified in all contexts, 0 in most, 0 context-dependent

Aliases: -c = --crown-margin, -g = --goal, -p = --prefix, -s = --split-only, -t = --tagged-paragraph, -u = --uniform-spacing, -w = --width

## Unique behavior (observable when tested alone)
  -g  # goal width (default of 93% of width)
    tested: "--goal=2" in passwd_minimal / stdin
    | flag adds 2 lines: a,b,c, d:e:f g h i
    | flag removes 1 lines: a,b,c d:e:f g h i
    without flag:
      a,b,c d:e:f g h i
    with flag:
      a,b,c
      d:e:f g h i
  -p  # reformat only lines beginning with STRING, reattaching the prefix to reformatted lines
    tested: "-p" "test" "input.txt" "other.txt" in numbers_standard / input.txt=size:1
    | flag adds 2 lines: xother content, second line
    | flag removes 2 lines: x, other content second line
    without flag:
      x
      other content second line
    with flag:
      xother content
      second line
  -w  # maximum line width (default of 75 columns)
    tested: "-w" "10" "input.txt" "other.txt" in words_minimal
    | flag adds 1381 lines: aardvark, abbreviation, about, abstract, accept
    | flag removes 151 lines: aardvark abbreviation about abstract accept accepted accepting access, accommodate acknowledge across Africa afternoon again against aggregate, ahead algorithm Alice all already also although always Amazon American, among an and another answer Apache apostrophe Apple application, approximately architect Argentina around arrange Asia assembly
    without flag:
      aardvark abbreviation about abstract accept accepted accepting access
      accommodate acknowledge across Africa afternoon again against aggregate
      ahead algorithm Alice all already also although always Amazon American
      among an and another answer Apache apostrophe Apple application
      approximately architect Argentina around arrange Asia assembly
      at Australia available awkward azure back balance banana bandwidth
            ... (145 more)
    with flag:
      aardvark
      abbreviation
      about
      abstract
      accept
      accepted
            ... (1375 more)

## Distinguishable in combination (verified via flag pairs)
  -c  # preserve indentation of first two lines
    | flag adds 24 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin, sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice, Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob
    | flag removes 11 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob Smith,Room 42,x1234,:/home/bob:/bin/zsh, charlie:x:1002:1002:Charlie Brown:/home/charlie:/bin/bash, diana:x:1003:1003:Diana Prince:/home/diana:/usr/bin/fish
    | 20 lines unchanged
    proven via: (pairwise evidence)
  -s  # split long lines, but do not refill
    | flag adds 24 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin, sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice, Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob
    | flag removes 11 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob Smith,Room 42,x1234,:/home/bob:/bin/zsh, charlie:x:1002:1002:Charlie Brown:/home/charlie:/bin/bash, diana:x:1003:1003:Diana Prince:/home/diana:/usr/bin/fish
    | 20 lines unchanged
    proven via: (pairwise evidence)
  -t  # indentation of first line different from second
    | flag adds 6 lines:    000.00,    000,    000.00,    000,00,    000
    | flag removes 6 lines: 000.00, 000, 000.00, 000,00, 000
    | 71 lines unchanged
    proven via: (pairwise evidence)
  -u  # one space between words, two after sentences
    | flag adds 24 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin, sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice, Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob
    | flag removes 11 lines: sys:x:3:3:sys:/dev:/usr/sbin/nologin sync:x:4:65534:sync:/bin:/bin/sync, alice:x:1000:1000:Alice Johnson,,,:/home/alice:/bin/bash, bob:x:1001:1001:Bob Smith,Room 42,x1234,:/home/bob:/bin/zsh, charlie:x:1002:1002:Charlie Brown:/home/charlie:/bin/bash, diana:x:1003:1003:Diana Prince:/home/diana:/usr/bin/fish
    | 20 lines unchanged
    proven via: (pairwise evidence)

